r old friend Hong Kong be forced to send &pound;50Bn to China. Now they&rsquo;re seeking our help for democracy and freedom, be brave and stand up for Hong Kong!<br />\n之後再講&pound;50Bn可以fund NHS幾多幾多，英國海外軍費幾多幾多，dog whistle 引導佢地覺得嗰啲錢可以畀佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad308d6e735f7240669942339453ee087741024","tid":1284262,"uid":41245,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T06:03:16.000Z","msg":"IT&rsquo;S A SHAME TO OUR NATION NOT TO PROTECT OUR OLD FRIEND HONG KONG!"},{"pid":"c90d10efbe0d7f125650097107e66f5c85293321","tid":1284262,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cad308d6e735f7240669942339453ee087741024","tid":1284262,"uid":41245,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T06:03:16.000Z","msg":"IT&rsquo;S A SHAME TO OUR NATION NOT TO PROTECT OUR OLD FRIEND HONG KONG!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T06:04:38.000Z","msg":"依啲放料畀the sun, dailymail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb412da35ebc80712c58124aaf11799c94681e7","tid":1284262,"uid":4739,"like":87,"dislike":1,"score":86,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T06:30:07.000Z","msg":"標題黨<br />\n英國衛報已報警犬 拉左義士"},{"pid":"55abe258d52651b03bb771c71ae1c8d2970e0f1b","tid":1284262,"uid":250951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T06:35:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/GzfbXtQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGzfbXtQ.png&h=4e59ec53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c44aab2694fe8c36a8b4e4006bb965153b2e071","tid":1284262,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T06:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />畀晒歐美知道<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gHZTsAA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.